SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 6
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THERE ARE TWO MAJOR CLASSES OF MEMBERS, GENERAL FULL-VOTING MEMBERS AND NON-VOTING MEMBERS. GENERAL FULL-VOTING MEMBERS ARE THE MEMBERS THAT PAY ALL THEIR INITIATION FEES IN FULL. THESE MEMBERS HAVE THE AUTHORITY TO ELECT THE GOVERNING BODY AND ALSO APPROVE SIGNIFICANT DECISIONS MADE BY THE GOVERNING BODY. EXAMPLES OF THESE SIGNIFICANT DECISIONS COULD INCLUDE THE APPROVAL OF ASSESSMENTS AND APPROVAL OF RAISING DUES IN A GIVEN YEAR. THE NON-VOTING MEMBER CLASS INCLUDES THE REMAINING MEMBERS WHO DO NOT HAVE THE AUTHORITY TO ELECT THE GOVERNING BODY OR APPROVE ANY SIGNIFICANT DECISIONS MADE BY THE GOVERNING BODY.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 7A
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: IN CASE OF A VACANCY IN THE OFFICE OF PRESIDENT, VICE-PRESIDENT, SECRETARY, OR TREASURER, OR IN THE POSITION OF A DIRECTOR, THE GOVERNING BOARD SHALL FILL SUCH VACANCY BY APPOINTMENT. THE APPOINTMENT SHALL BE FOR THE PERIOD OF TIME REMAINING UNTIL THE NEXT ANNUAL MEETING OF THE CLUB, AT WHICH TIME ANY DIRECTOR'S POSITION FOR WHICH AN UNEXPIRED TERM REMAINS SHALL BE FILLED BY ELECTION.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 7B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE GENERAL FULL-VOTING MEMBERS HAVE THE RIGHT TO RATIFY SIGNIFICANT DECISIONS MADE BY THE BOARD MEMBERS. EXAMPLES OF THESE SIGNIFICANT DECISIONS COULD INCLUDE THE APPROVAL OF ASSESSMENTS AND APPROVAL OF RAISING DUES IN A GIVEN YEAR.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: AFTER THE FORM 990 IS PREPARED BY AN OUTSIDE CPA FIRM, FRAZIER & DEETER, LLC, THE FORM IS FIRST REVIEWED BY THE CFO FOR ACCURACY. THE FORM IS THEN PRESENTED TO THE FULL BOARD OF DIRECTORS AND THEN SIGNED BY THE PRESIDENT.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THERE IS A REPORT GIVEN ANNUALLY OF ALL PURCHASE TRANSACTIONS TO ALL MEMBERS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THERE IS AN ANNUAL PERFORMANCE REVIEW OF ALL MANAGEMENT. IF THERE IS AN INCREASE IN THE ANNUAL PERFORMANCE REVIEW THEN THERE IS A STANDARD COMPENSATION INCREASE FOR ALL MANAGEMENT.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: DOCUMENTS ARE AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST AND CAN BE REVIEWED AT THE CLUB.
